Vulkan Reference license policy

This repository uses separate licenses for software code and documentation
content.

1. Software code

   Unless otherwise stated, source code and build assets in this repository are
   licensed under the MIT License. See LICENSE-CODE.

   This includes:
   - assets/
   - lib/
   - scripts/
   - package.json and package-lock.json
   - site.json
   - repository configuration files

2. Documentation and reference content

   Documentation and reference content are licensed under the Creative Commons
   Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License. See
   LICENSE-CONTENT.

   This includes:
   - content/
   - README.md documentation sections
   - generated documentation content embedded in dist/

3. Generated output

   Files in dist/ are generated from both software code and documentation
   content. The code/assets portions remain under the MIT License. The embedded
   documentation/reference content remains under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.

4. Third-party dependencies

   Third-party dependencies keep their own licenses.

